assignments.name: 10.0 ASSIGNMENT: Question of the Week (Due October 31)
assignments.intro:
Question of the Week (1 point)

Learning Objective: I can answer the question of the week that was asked during the Live Session.

After attending the Live Session or watching the recording you can complete this assignment. On this assignment, you will submit your answer to the "Question of the Week" that was posed in the live session. 


  • You will have 1 attempt on this assignment.

Click Attempt Quiz Now to begin the assignment.

If you need to stop working on your assignment for any reason, click Finish Attempt (in the upper right corner of the quiz navigation page) and it will save your work. You will be able to return to your attempt and complete your answers.
